Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:02.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:04.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nerve signals in the brain are always depicted like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:04.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,大脑里的神经信号总是被描绘成这种样子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:07.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,But, what is actually going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:07.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是，究竟发生了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:10.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, if you open a textbook, it's this complicated mechanism:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:10.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果你翻开课本  会看到一堆复杂的机制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:14.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,potentials, many different ions, chemical and electrical gradients...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:14.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,动作电位、各种离子一大堆、化学成分和带电的成分……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:20.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,But, the basic principle of how nerve signals work is actually very straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:20.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,不过  神经信号基本的工作原理  其实非常简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.43,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(660,166)\fad(500,300)\c&Hc0ccd0&}细胞体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:20.43,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(1090,800)\fad(500,300)\c&H000000&}细胞过程（轴突）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:25.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, I came up with a model that's using marbles that you can understand intuitively.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:25.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以  我用弹珠搞了个模型  你就能直观地感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:26.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(550,250)\fad(150,100)\c&H6518a4&}弹{\fsp-20}珠{\fsp0}（离子）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(885,210)\fad(150,100)\fad(100,100)\c&H43b178&}通道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(1290,250)\fad(150,100)\fad(100,100)\c&Ha76b32&}电{\fsp-20}梯{\fsp0}（离子泵）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,走起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, the cell puts out a few marbles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,细胞先放进来一小批弹珠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,and if there's enough of them, they can trigger a channel to open and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:31.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,一旦弹珠数量足够  就能触发一个通道开启
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:36.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,more marbles pour in and are immediately pumped back out by the elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:36.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,让更多的弹珠进来  再通过电梯来泵回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:38.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,But a few reach the next section,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:38.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,但还有少部分弹珠到了下一个通道处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,where they trigger the next channel and more marbles pour in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们会触发了下一个通道  又让更多弹珠进来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they spread further, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些弹珠会跑得更远 以此类推
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:47.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,So, this way, the signal travels on until it reaches the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:47.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,信号通过这样一直传递下去  直至到达终点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:50.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the basic principle of nerve signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:50.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,这就是神经信号的基本原理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,And as long as you're alive, that is, as long as the elevators are working,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,只要你还有一口气  或者说“电梯”还能工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,this can repeat over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,大脑里的信号就会不断在传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:59.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,So now, next time you see this, you know what's really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:59.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,下次你再见到这种动画时  你就知道是在干啥了
